message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE". This is because the paper discusses a new approach for open-domain question answering using pre-trained language models, which falls under the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
